    openedCardTitle: Yeti
    openedCardTitleKey: YETI
    openedCardFrontDescription: "<b>Character:</b> Yeti\n<b>Represents:</b> Australopithecus\n<b>Era:</b>
      Pliocene to early Pleistocene\n<b>Time:</b> about 4.4 to 1.4 million years
      ago\n<b>Status:</b> Extinct\n<b>Size:</b> 1 to 1.5 meters tall\n\n<b>Focus:</b>
      \nBone function, balance, and movement."
    openedCardFrontDescriptionKey: REWARD_YETI_FRONT
    openedCardBackDescription: "In this mission, you matched each bone or structure
      by its function. Bones are not only shapes \u2014 they help bodies move, balance,
      and stand."
    openedCardBackDescriptionKey: REWARD_YETI_BACK
